    "encid": "-BSGJc6Z42tsNwLkgrDyOQ",
    "text": {
      "full": "The overall atmosphere and vibe was awesome! I liked that you could see the kitchen and all of the spirit bottles on the shelves. The service was so incredibly friendly as well. The Tellicherry chicken & Gouda pasta was very delicious. The best comparison I can pair with it is \"Marry Me Chicken.\" Others in our party got the Mac & cheese, the mushroom pasta, and a cheeseburger and they were also pleased with their meals. If you're looking for a place with good drinks and a hearty meal, this is your place!",
      "language": "en"
    },
