    "encid": "nIqAkLKE1GyfflUcbrTIJg",
    "text": {
      "full": "I don't know if I'm the only one who daydreams about how good the food is going to be in Heaven.  If you've ever thought about it...Go to Von's 1000 Spirits.  Olga our server was the best.  Her energy, kindness and menu suggestions made this place one of my favorite places to eat when traveling to Seattle.  The ambiance, crowd, location and vibe was everything!  I'd love to own a place like this.",
